Package entity

Class ResourceNodeMetricsEntity

java.lang.Object
entity.ResourceNodeMetricsEntity
@Entity public class ResourceNodeMetricsEntity extends Object
Entity class representing metrics of a resource node in a specific country on a given day. This class is mapped to the "resource_node_metrics" table and contains details such as maximum capacity, production cost, and tier of the resource node.
